  "instructions": [
    "preheat the air fryer to 400°f (200°c).",
    "in a large bowl, whisk together cumin, coriander, paprika, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper.",
    "add the chicken to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "add the sliced shallots, red bell pepper, and carrots to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "spray the air fryer basket with olive oil and add the chicken and vegetable mixture.",
    "cook for 15 minutes, shaking the basket halfway through.",
    "remove the chicken and vegetables from the air fryer and transfer to a serving dish.",
    "sprinkle with chopped parsley and serve immediately.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
  ],
